description: Associates an Amazon Web Services account with an Amazon Inspector delegated administrator. An HTTP 200 response indicates the association was successfully started, but doesn't indicate whether it was completed. You can check if the association completed by using ListMembers for multiple accounts or GetMembers for a single account.

parameters.name: accountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the member account to be associated.

nested_items.name: accountId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID of the successfully associated member account.
